              "type": "richtext",
              "name": "Richtext",
              "settings": {
                "title": "<p><strong>It's never a single method, only a single goal: to increase absorption. </strong>Using proprietary, game-changing technology and ingredients in their most absorbable form, we create pharmaceutical-grade  supplements with up to 149x more absorption.</p><p></p><p>We are continuously engaged in researching, testing, and verifying results. We source or create the most bioavailable ingredients humanly possible. In an industry with false credibility, we look to science for solutions. Read more about why supplements fail to absorb and our approach to solving this problem below.</p>",
