                    "richtext_hzQpYM": {
                      "type": "richtext",
                      "name": "Richtext",
                      "settings": {
                        "title": "<h2><strong>Introducing Capsoil</strong><em><strong>®</strong></em><strong>Technology.</strong></h2><p>Capsoil<em><strong>®</strong></em> Technology’s proprietary process improves upon traditional lipid nanotechnology and transforms both water-soluble and fat-soluble bioactives into their most bioavailable forms.</p><p></p><p>Capsoil<em><strong>®</strong></em> liposomes are produced through a process that creates robust, high-potency liposomal structures. These can be dried into a water-soluble powder, designed to provide enhanced stability during digestion. Capsoil<em><strong>®</strong></em> Powders, alternatively, stem from a unique process that converts fat-soluble bioactives into a water-soluble powder. Creating a complete self-emulsifying lipid nanoparticle without the use of solvents, chemicals, or enzymes, preserving the integrity and potency of each nutrient. Demonstrated to increase bioavailability by 90%-985%*,</p><p></p><p>Capsoil<em><strong>®</strong></em> Technology is dedicated to revolutionizing the way nutrients are delivered. This innovative approach is reshaping the future of dietary supplements, making Capsoil<em><strong>® </strong></em>Technology a leader in the field of nutritional science.</p>",
                        "text_alignment": "inherit",
                        "content_class": "richtext-md",
                        "text_color": "",
                        "custom_css": "& h2{\n   margin-bottom: 32px;\n}\n\n\n\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  & h2{\n    margin-bottom: 16px;\n  }\n}",
